Entry.JapaneseText: この力、すばらしい…… これが本格稼動すれば、 戦局は我が方へ転がる
Entry.EnglishText: This power is fantastic... With this on the field we will surely have the upper hand in the war!

Entry.JapaneseText: この力があれば、 エリュシオンを統べることすら、 可能かもしれないな
Entry.EnglishText: With this weapon...taking control of Elysium will be rather easy.

Entry.JapaneseText: ダオスの、ですか。 それはまた大きく出ましたな
Entry.EnglishText: Dhaos is still on our way, though. That's a big factor.

Entry.JapaneseText: まぁ、いいではないですか、 ふぉふぉ……
Entry.EnglishText: He might as well not be, now. Hahahahaha!

Entry.JapaneseText: よくやったな、メルティア。 おまえの頭脳は明日を開く力だ
Entry.EnglishText: You have done well <MEL>tia. Thanks to your intellect we will be able to secure a better future for everyone.

Entry.JapaneseText: ありがとうございます、 お父様
礼を言うのはこちらの方だ。 おまえの父親でよかったよ
Entry.EnglishText: The one who should be thanking is me. I am so very glad to be your father.

Entry.JapaneseText: これで我々はエリュシオンを、 あのダオスにすら対抗できる力を 手にしたのだからな
Entry.EnglishText: With this you granted us the capability to stand against Elysium and Dhaos on the battlefield.

Entry.JapaneseText: 決戦は<Red>ウェーランド<White>だ。 既にディオス率いる部隊は 現地に待機している
Entry.EnglishText: Right now <DIO>s is leading the army into a decisive fight in Wayland.

Entry.JapaneseText: 博士、マナの消費量について 気になることが……
Entry.EnglishText: Doctor, would you please see this? The amount of used Mana is off-charts...this is rather unsettling...
Is it really something we should worry about...?

Entry.JapaneseText: いえ、そうでは ないのですが……
じゃあ構わないわ。 実験は成功よ
Entry.EnglishText: Then there's no problem. The experiment was a success.

Entry.JapaneseText: 構わない…… お父様が喜んでくださるなら……
Entry.EnglishText: There's no problem.... Because father finally acknowledged me...

Entry.JapaneseText: お父様が私を愛して下されば、 私を、必要として下されば
Entry.EnglishText: I need father's love to continue forward and I would do anything he says just for him...
